---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
---
<Site title={'agents — rega rega'}>
<Fragment set:html={'<section class="doc-wrap">\n  <div class="meta-line"><span class="dot"></span>— for agents &amp; partners</div>\n  <h1>work with us as an <em>agent</em>.</h1>\n  <div class="updated">— commission 10% · georgia</div>\n\n  <p class="lede">If you\'re an agent and your client wants to <b>buy property in Batumi</b>, <b>rent it out long-term</b>, or <b>have it managed by an operator</b> — bring them to us. We\'ll close the deal together and pay your commission.</p>\n\n  <h2>what we do</h2>\n  <p>bre runs short and mid-term rental apartments in Batumi. We help foreign owners buy and manage their flats — from picking a building to renovation, furnishing, and turning the unit into a working asset. We also run a city guide that we point our guests to.</p>\n\n  <h2>who we work with</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>independent real estate agents in Georgia and abroad</li>\n    <li>relocation specialists and family offices</li>\n    <li>concierge services and lifestyle managers</li>\n    <li>brokers who already have a client looking at Batumi seriously</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>commission</h2>\n  <p><b>10% of our fee</b>, paid after we close the deal and our side is paid. We pay by bank transfer, in USD or local currency. No paperwork beyond a one-page agreement on first transaction. Repeat referrals — even simpler.</p>\n\n  <h2>what you do</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>introduce the client to us by email or Telegram — short intro, what they\'re looking for, budget</li>\n    <li>stay in the loop or step back — your call</li>\n    <li>we keep you posted on the deal status</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>what we do</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>full management: building selection, due diligence, purchase, renovation, furnishing</li>\n    <li>operating the rental once it\'s ready (Airbnb, Booking, direct)</li>\n    <li>monthly accounting and reports to the owner</li>\n    <li>transparent fees: 20% of net rental income, no surprise charges</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>how it starts</h2>\n  <p>Send us the intro — name, contact, what they need, and any context you think helps. We reply within a day, hop on a call, and take it from there. Confidentiality goes without saying.</p>\n\n  <div class="end">Ready to partner? Write us at <a href="mailto:hello@bre.ge">hello@bre.ge</a> or in <a href="https://t.me/bre_ge">Telegram</a>. Let\'s talk.</div>\n</section>'} />
<style is:global set:html={'.doc-wrap{padding:140px 28px 80px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}\n.meta-line{font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}\n.meta-line .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--page)}\n.doc-wrap .updated{margin-top:18px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap .lede{margin-top:32px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap .lede b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}\n.doc-wrap h2{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:24px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-top:48px;text-transform:lowercase}\n.doc-wrap p{margin-top:14px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap p b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}\n.doc-wrap ul{margin-top:14px;padding-left:0;list-style:none}\n.doc-wrap ul li{padding-left:18px;position:relative;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:8px}\n.doc-wrap ul li::before{content:\'—\';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--page)}\n.doc-wrap .end{margin-top:64px;padding:24px;background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n.doc-wrap .end a{color:var(--page);font-weight:600}\n@media (max-width:880px){\n.doc-wrap{padding:100px 14px 48px}\n}'}></style>
</Site>
